information.transcription:
This firm was founded in 1825 by Daniel Appleton at 200
Greenwich St., in buildings destroyed by the fire of
1835. The present location is 34 Leonard St.

D. Appleton & Co. are importers, publishers, booksellers,
manufacturers of blank books, and wholesale stationers
Their specialties are Appleton's School Books, Games,
and Sporting Goods.

Lith in U.S.A. July 28—04
C.C.
